  <section>
    <h2>Browser Support</h2>
    <p>The <code>&lt;summary&gt;</code> element is supported in all modern browsers. The <code>::marker</code> pseudo-element has varying support for customization, which is why Vanilla Breeze uses <code>::after</code> for the chevron indicator.</p>
